<br>
I can't begin to count how many normal mobs we did up there.  I never saw the Staff of Elemental Mastery: Earth drop from anyone other than Magi P'Tasa.<br>
<br>
There seems to be a lot of confusion by non mages about a mage staff up there that drops from other mobs (i.e. other Minis like Mistress of Scorn).  That 2nd mage staff in Hate is Staff of Elemental Mastery: Fire.<br>
<br>
Everyone who is ignorant of the magician epic quest tends to get those two items confused.  I can forgive that kind of error, but one time I was a little mad because the raid leader assumed it was the epic one and hadn't told the raid beforehand he was going to claim it for a MQ.  I saw a Staff of Elemental Mastery: Fire get looted by a druid lol and go to waste because they were greedy and ignorant.  *sigh* hehe<br>
<br>
Hope it helps.<br>
<br>
- Cae <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=allaakzamm>Allaa KZamm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 143<br> <font color=#333333>(10/29/02 12:00:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1471.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What drops the hate staff?</span><hr size=1>   I lost out on a Fire Staff just this Saturday due to that.  The person leading the raid thought it was an Earth Staff (which I have) and gave the loot to another pickup mage who was trying out for our allies guild.  It was rough, but sometimes you just gotta take one on the chin.<br>
<br>
