<br>
/agree<br>
<br>
Only Magi P'Tasa (and possibly Inny - been trying to get confirmation of that for months - I've only seen him once) drops the Earth staff.<br>
<br>
I was just saying that if there are posts out there that talk about the staff dropping off of other mobs in Hate in addition to Magi P'Tasa they are probably confused and that confusion could have been tied into the Fire Staff.  If people only had a vague recollection of the quest (non mages) and see a No Drop staff with almost the exact same name as the one for our epic they might be justified in the reason for their posts; I can kind of understand how this can happen.<br>
<br>
Earlier comment about the Fire staff wasn't really meant to be completely a hijack hehe (but ... saw that fire staff drop 3 three times and I got mine the third time during a scheduled raid that coincidently coincided with patch day; one of the two KS guilds that ran over us upstairs took down Mistress of Spite and since I had been on some of that guilds open raids before I knew their default hate raid chat channel and was watching it - hehe see helps to go on lots of raids.  I ran right up there and asked if I could have it since they were only there for ranger stones.  Damn still can't believe there were three raids going on at the same time all competing for Minis that night.  Hate sucks!  Haven't really been back since).<br>
<br>
- Cae<br>
